##### RECIPE ENDPOINTS #####

### Get all recipes
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes

### Get hidden recipes
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes/hidden

### Get recipe by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes/6a12725ce48f57ecc71efbea

### Get recipes by tag
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes/tag/test

### Get recipes by name
GET http://localhost:3000/recipes/name/hummus

### Create a recipe
POST http://localhost:3000/recipes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test Recipe",
  "ingredients": [
    { "text": "1 cup flour" },
    { "text": "2 eggs", "optional": true }
  ],
  "steps": [
    "Mix ingredients",
    "Bake at 350F for 20 minutes"
  ],
  "tags": ["test", "baking"]
}

### Update a recipe
PUT http://localhost:3000/recipes/6a12725ce48f57ecc71efbea
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Recipe Title"
}

### Delete a recipe
DELETE http://localhost:3000/recipes/6a12725ce48f57ecc71efbea

